  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This clinical trial is aimed to show a procalcitonin-guided treatment algorithm may shorten
      duration of antibiotic therapy safely and cost-effectively in sepsis patients of Korean ICU.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
